488
00:18:30,610 --> 00:18:32,811
and it's just like...
just the tiniest bit out of sync

489
00:18:32,812 --> 00:18:34,480
so you just barely notice it?

490
00:18:34,481 --> 00:18:39,451
Mm-hmm.
All right, Emma?

