00:18:45,892 --> 00:18:47,559
Hello.

494
00:18:47,560 --> 00:18:48,761
Yeah, it is echoing,

495
00:18:48,762 --> 00:18:49,895
like you had a shot...

496
00:18:49,896 --> 00:18:51,463
like you had a shot of vodka.

497
00:18:51,464 --> 00:18:53,298
- [LAUGHING]
- Something like that, like...

498
00:18:53,299 --> 00:18:55,934
Yeah, acute audio distortion
is really common.

499
00:18:55,935 --> 00:18:57,269
Okay.

500
00:18:57,270 --> 00:19:00,205
Here we see a classic example
of conformity.

501
00:19:00,206 --> 00:19:02,441
But is she just trying
to fit in

502
00:19:02,442 --> 00:19:04,143
or does she truly believe

503
