505
00:19:08,648 --> 00:19:10,616
I feel kind of, like,
just relaxed.

506
00:19:10,617 --> 00:19:12,451
I just feel, like,
really relaxed.

507
00:19:12,452 --> 00:19:15,521
She's now claiming to feel
multiple side effects.

508
00:19:15,522 --> 00:19:16,822
But yeah, no, it's like I...

509
00:19:16,823 --> 00:19:18,457
I had, like, two drinks
or something.

510
00:19:18,458 --> 00:19:20,192
Right, and in this moment now,

511
00:19:20,193 --> 00:19:21,427
how do you feel?

512
00:19:21,428 --> 00:19:23,228
- Uh, kind of tired.
- Tired.

513
00:19:23,229 --> 00:19:24,997
- Right?
- Yeah.

514
00:19:24,998 --> 00:19:26,498
- Am I the only one?
- No. [LAUGHS]

515
00:19:26,499 --> 00:19:29,601
Should we go, like, nap on
that bean bag?

516
00:19:29,602 --> 00:19:31,270
Emma continues
to look to the group

517
00:19:31,271 --> 00:19:32,838
for reassurance
that her symptoms

518
00:19:32,839 --> 00:19:34,239
are in line with theirs.

519
00:19:34,240 --> 00:19:35,474
I don't know if I like it.

520
00:19:35,475 --> 00:19:36,542
I can't decide.

521
00:19:36,543 --> 00:19:37,910
You know what I mean?

522
00:19:37,911 --> 00:19:39,511
What do you guys think?
I don't know.

523
00:19:39,512 --> 00:19:41,280
Whatever she thinks
she's feeling,

524
00:19:41,281 --> 00:19:43,649
she wants to make sure
it fits in with the group.

525
00:19:43,650 --> 00:19:45,317
The room is warmer, no?

526
00:19:45,318 --> 00:19:46,952
Yeah.

527
00:19:46,953 --> 00:19:50,689
Would you take this while you
