528
00:19:50,690 --> 00:19:52,324
No, I don't think so.

529
00:19:52,325 --> 00:19:54,526
Because...

530
00:19:54,527 --> 00:19:57,363
'Cause you need to concentrate
on what you're doing.

531
00:19:57,364 --> 00:19:59,665
But I just feel so relaxed.

